{"type": "article", "id": 10151, "title": "你“骑着”行李箱飞驰而过，只留一个潇洒的背影", "description": "骑着行李箱赶飞机，棒呆了", "date": "2015-05-29T08:10:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10820, "name": "有趣"}, {"id": 2381, "name": "行李箱"}, {"id": 1181, "name": "中国"}, {"id": 10821, "name": "suitsupply"}], "category": 18, "column": null, "author": 112316, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604221457vHwFPaIp6S3Ae21f.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t看着别人拖着行李箱在龟速前进时，你“骑着”行李箱飞驰而过，只留给他们一个潇洒的背影，这感觉听起来很不错。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604221454kSzVM0Th35nvj4XQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55555556\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t最近，欧洲时尚男装品牌 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Suitsup</span>ply <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">推出了一款兼具滑板车功能的行李箱，命名为“</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">The Race Case.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”，每只售价 </span>599 <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美元。这个以“树立自我，而非迎合大众”为文化核心的品牌在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2013 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">4 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月开通针对中国市场的官方销售平台，提供全球 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日送达，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">30 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日免费上门退换服务。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t在其<a href=\"http://cn.suitsupply.com/zh/bags/theracecase/ST001.html\">中国官网</a>上显示，这款行李箱售价 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">3880 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元人民币</span> ，尺寸为 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">51x37x26 cm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，采用深棕色小牛皮制成。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t这是它的皮质“方向盘”：</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604221455rGd8SzDEh3qIsYmU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t坚实的滑板车底部：</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604221455zxTEb4OiqgYchpr0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t它可以叠起来：</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604221456K8S6aJZIExlmicFH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t不管多么酷炫，它还保持着一个行李箱应有的自我修养：</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604221456Tr5PvBqMfJ42XxGF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t说了这么多，这个酷酷的家伙恐怕已经让很多人动心了。</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t那么问题来了，前面行李那么重，确定不会让骑着它奔驰的男（<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">dou</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）生（</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">bi</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）摔倒吗？是不是应该搭配个头盔呢？</span>Suitsupply <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">对 </span><a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/the-race-case-is-beautiful-but-useless-2015-5\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Business Insider </a> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">表示这款产品他们已经测试了一年，公司团队能够保证这是一款实用型商品。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">感受一下：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604221457cDOy9WJGjaPKAm5p.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55555556\" data-format=\"gif\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}